cs.CV, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.GR, cs.MM

This paper is primarily focused on improving the quality of generative images, which falls under the computer vision (cs.CV) and machine learning (cs.LG) categories. The paper also proposes changes to the model architecture and training methods, which are related to artificial intelligence (cs.AI) and graphics (cs.GR). Additionally, the paper includes visualizations of the generator's output resolution, which could be considered multimedia (cs.MM).
